Doc","id":"ida74f9f25-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Executive Documents","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"delegationOfFunctions","id":"ida74f9f26-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Delegation of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Functions of President under this section delegated to Secretary of Defense, see section 1(11) of Ex. Ord. No. 11390, ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1968-01-22"},"text":"Jan. 22, 1968","children":[],"tail":", 33 F.R. 841, set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t3/s301"},"text":"section 301 of Title 3","children":[],"tail":", The President."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"ida74f9f27-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Delegation of Authority","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Authority of President under this section as invoked by sections 2 and 3 of Ex. Ord. No. 13223, ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2001-09-14"},"text":"Sept. 14, 2001","children":[],"tail":", 66 F.R. 48201, as amended, delegated to Secretary of Defense by section 4 of Ex. Ord. No. 13223, and authority of President under this section as invoked by section 2 of Ex. Ord. No. 13223 delegated to Secretary of Homeland Security by section 5 of Ex. Ord. No. 13223, as amended, set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s12302"},"text":"section 12302 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
